If there’s interest, I’d love to connect with others who want to brainstorm ideas, structure a hackathon, or work on projects together. 🚀

@undefined @undefined @undefined and others that plan to stay at NS longer than 30 days, would recommend checking out the Malaysian Digital Nomad Visa page in the NS wiki at [ns.com/wiki](https://ns.com/wiki). 

While you wait to hear back on your visa application, you can go to Singapore/Indonesia before the end of 30 days (if that's your maximum visa-free stay allowed) to reset the clock before you come back to Malaysia again.

Note: to access the wiki, you must (a) be an accepted member and (b) have completed the onboarding form you were emailed.

I also need help with getting the Malaysian Visa. 


